title: Georgia national under-19 football team
text:
The Georgian national under-19 football team is the national under-19 <a href="Football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> team of <a href="Georgia%20%28country%29">Georgia</a> and is controlled by the <a href="Georgian%20Football%20Federation">Georgian Football Federation</a>.In this team play most talented Georgian Footballers under 19 years.
Current squad.
Squad selection for the <a href="2015%20UEFA%20European%20Under-19%20Championship%20qualification">2015 UEFA European Under-19 Championship qualification</a> in May 2014.
